        "body": "Let $`W` be the random variable of the number of pies that are\nunsatisfactory out of $` 50 `\nand let $`p` be the probability that a randomly chosen\npie is unsatisfactory\n\n$$`  W \\sim \\mathrm{B} (50, p ) `\n\nBy considering $` \\mathrm{E} \\left( W \\right), `\n\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\"><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>p</mi><mo>≈</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">∑</mo><mi>f</mi><mi>w</mi></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">∑</mo><mi>f</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>50</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>≈</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>9</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>5</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>80</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mn>50</mn><mi>p</mi><mo>≈</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>≈</mo><mn>0.0125</mn><mspace width=\"0.2778em\"></mspace><mi>∎</mi></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{gather*} np \\approx  \\frac{\\sum fw}{\\sum f}\n\t\\\\ \\left( 50 \\right)p \\approx  \\frac{0 + \\left( 1 \\right)\\left( 9 \\right) + \\left( 2 \\right)\\left( 6 \\right) + \\left( 3 \\right)\\left( 4 \\right) + \\left( 4 \\right)\\left( 3 \\right) + \\left( 5 \\right)\\left( 1 \\right)}{80}\n\t\\\\ 50p \\approx  \\frac{5}{8}\n\t\\\\ p \\approx  0.0125 \\; \\QED\n\\end{gather*}\n```\n"
