          {
            "body": "Let $`D` denote the random variable of the number of days in which\nfewer than 3 burgers have insufficient cheese in them out of $` 28 `\n\n$$` D \\sim \\mathrm{B} \\left( 28, 0.29844 \\right) `\n\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\" columnalign=\"right left\"><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">E</mi></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mi>D</mi><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>28</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>0.29844</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>8.3562</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>8.36</mn><mtext> days (3 s.f.)</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2778em\"></mspace><mi>∎</mi></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{align*} & \\mathrm{E} \\left( D \\right)\n\t\\\\ &= np\n\t\\\\ &= \\left( 28 \\right)\\left( 0.29844 \\right)\n\t\\\\ &= 8.3562 \\\\ &= 8.36 \\text{ days (3 s.f.)} \\; \\QED\n\\end{align*}\n```\n"
          },
