            "body": "Let $`T` denote the random variable of the number of burgers\nfound to have insufficient cheese in them out of $` {120 \\times  28 = 3360} `\nburgers in $` 28 `\ndays\n\n$$` T \\sim \\mathrm{B} \\left( 3360, 0.03 \\right) `\n\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\" columnalign=\"right left\"><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mi>T</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>100</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mi>T</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>100</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.50578</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.506</mn><mtext> (3 s.f.)</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2778em\"></mspace><mi>∎</mi></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{align*} & \\mathrm{P} \\left( T > 100 \\right)\n\t\\\\ &= 1 - \\mathrm{P} \\left( T \\leq 100 \\right)\n\t\\\\ &= 0.50578 \\\\ &= 0.506 \\text{ (3 s.f.)} \\; \\QED\n\\end{align*}\n```\n"
